                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, daz er zu dem
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> im Hof, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> iht zu
                                <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, so
